{"tid":2183333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Pompeo:侵正在考慮限制中共國留學生簽證","createTime":"2020-09-01T01:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T03:17:31.000Z","uid":294518,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d594732125a34d55ba8e03afbef49e860320e8","tid":2183333,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"侵正在考慮限制中共國留學生簽證<br />\n蓬佩奧週一接受採訪時表示，川普總統正在權衡限制中共國學生來美留學。<br />\n蓬佩奧被問是否應該一段時間內不再讓更多中國學生進入美國時說，他不想在川普總統作出決定前評論，但川普政府可能會在未來幾周和幾個月內宣佈針對北京的新行動。<br />\n<br />\nPompeo says Trump looking at whether to restrict Chinese students from the US<br />\n<a href=\"https://thehill.com/policy/international/514429-pompeo-says-trump-looking-at-whether-to-restrict-chinese-students-from\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Finternational%2F514429-pompeo-says-trump-looking-at-whether-to-restrict-chinese-students-from&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7h%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=dfa7c32c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thehill.com/policy/international/514429-pompeo-says-trump-looking-at-whether-to-restrict-chinese-students-from</a>"},{"pid":"c60b3be6fd960d4ef372859d6da69505ee7768e7","tid":2183333,"uid":191926,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"隨時包埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e974a2c2f21c7d8bb6eef05289f45cb5e60343d","tid":2183333,"uid":7323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">一定要啊</span>"},{"pid":"10902855faed46f83701c1d2821c37364d40b8b9","tid":2183333,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283c135c0207131efbb1fe0980b393488fed2c79","tid":2183333,"uid":48485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,